duff
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:boiled or steamed suet pudding, often with dried fruit in it; a plum pudding.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: (mainly early outdoor and farming usage)
